\id JAS - Mpoto Bible Version
\h Yakobo
\toc1 Baluwa jejalembakike na Yakobo
\toc2 Yakobo
\toc3 Yako
\mt2 Baluwa jejalembakiki na
\mt1 Yakobo
\imt1 Ulongulelo
\ip Chitabu chaka Yakobo chakalembakiki na mundu joalowakiki Yakobo. Iwezikana jonihoju nde Yokobo joakabhi nung'una waka Yesu joakabhi chiongozi wa likanisa la kutumbula, jumu wa iyongozi wa likanisa la kutumbula lelahengakiki ku Yelusalemu (Matendu 15:13). Mtumi Paulo kabhete akandohiki “nguzu” ja likanisa mu chitabu cha Bhagalatia 2:9. Bhasomi bha mambu gha Bibilia bhahobhalela kubha chitabu chaka Yokobo chakalembakiki ngati hyaka ya 50 baada ya kubhelakeka kwaka Yesu Kristo. Kwa kubha Yakobo akabhi chiongozi wa likanisa lelakabhi ku Yelusalemu, iwezikana chakaka kubha akalembiki chitabu hechi paakabhi atama mu muchi ghonihoghu.
\ip Yakobo achipwagha chitabu chaki kwa ndandi ja “makabila komi na ghagheli gha Izilaeli ghaghapechangini pundema pokapi,” (Sula 1:1). Mabholu ghaghabhi mu chitabu chaka Yakobo nde ghaghabhi na nyonjeka kwa Bhakristo bhokapi, nambu matumizi gha malobhi “makabila komi na ghabheli” ghatenda kubya na uwezekanu kubha Yakobo akabhi ajilembiki baluwa jenu kwa ndandi ja Bhakristo bhabhakabhi na asili ja Kiyahude. Kwa kubha chitabu hechi chakalembakiki kwa ndandi ja kubhahikila mapogha ghamaheli patalipatali gha bhasomaji, chitabu chenu chakahengiki lihengu la mambu ghamaheli patalipatali. Yakobo apala kujomalakela uhusianu ghoubhi pachilanda ja uhobhalelu na matendu. Uhobhalelu wa chakaka anaubhonakanaje mu matendu, (Sula 2:17). Kabhete akanakila kubhokana na kulangiha upendeleu kwa bhandu bhabhabhi na hindu yamaheli, (Sula 2:1-4), na kutupwaghila tukubha tabhangalifo kubhokana na ghala ghatupwagha, (Sula 3:1-12).
\iot Ghaghabhihomu
\io1 Yakobo abhalamukila bhasomaji bhaki mu, (Sula 1:1).
\io1 Kujomulela abhajeghela mtima Bhakristo bhahinakyaje pabhapeta mu mang'ahiku, (Sula 1:2-27).
\io1 Palongi jaki abhalandila ntundu molibheli lijambu lelibhapalika nakanopi kulangiha uhobhalelu kwa indela ja matendu, (Sula 2:1-26).
\io1 Kabhete alandila ntundu bholi malobhi ghaweza kubha na makili, (Sula 3:1-12).
\io1 Kabhete Yakobo alangiha ntundu mbulau jaka Chapanga mojibheli na ulekanganu na mbulau ja pundema, (Sula 3:13-4:10).
\io1 Kubhokela panihapa abhakanakila bhasomaji bhaki ngabhikubha bhandu bhabhalibhona, (Sula 4:11-5:6).
\io1 Yakobo ajomulela chitabu chaki, (Sula ja 5:7-20) kwa kubhoha malobhi gha papamu.
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Nepani Yakobo, mtumika waka Chapanga na waka Bambo Yesu Kristo.
\p Nundamukila mwehapa makabila komi na ghabheli ghaghapechangini pundema.
\s1 Uhobhalelu na mbulau
\p 
\v 2 Bhalongu bhango, mbyaje na chiheku nakanope pampata malengakeku patalipatali,
\v 3 kwa ndandi mmanyi kubha kulengakeka kwa uhobhalelu winu kuleta uhinakilu.
\v 4 Kuhinakila kwinu ngakwikubha na ujomukelo, nahuli mpata kukangamala na kutwelakeka kila chindu panga kukepakewa na chindu chokapi chela.
\v 5 Nambu ngati mundu jokapi akepakiwi na mbulau, na impalika kundobha Chapanga jombi anaampekyaje, kwa ndandi Chapanga abhapekeha bhandu bhokapi kwa umaheli na kwa wamboni.
\v 6 Nambu impalika kulobha kwa uhobhalelu panga na choghoi chokapi. Kwa ndandi mundu joabhi na choghoi alengana na majegha gha bahali ghaghatolakiki na mpongu na kulekaleka koni na koni.
\v 7 Mundu ngati jonihoju ngaiholakela kubha anapata chindu chokapi kuhuma kwaka Bambo.
\v 8 Mundu joabhi na maholalelu ghabheli muntima waki, ngacheaweza kujema wichu kwa ghokapi ghaaghahenga.
\s1 Uhochu na wamaheli wa hindu
\p 
\v 9 Mundu jwanga na cheu chokapi impalika kuhekalela kwa ndandi atehi kukwehakeka,
\v 10 na mwanahindu yamaheli impalika kuhekalela kwa ndandi atehi kuhelakeka. Maghambu anahobhaje ngati lilobha la mungonda.
\v 11 Kwa ndandi lyobha lipita na lyotu laki likali lijomeha na kughatinyiha mahamba, na malobha ghaki ghapolota na unyahi waki uyonangeka. Bhelabhela mwanahindu yamaheli najombi anayonangikaje mu mahengu ghaki.
\s1 Malengakeku na Mang'ahiku
\p 
\v 12 Mbanga mundu joahinakalila chikahi cha malengakeku, kwa ndandi anajomwi kupeta mu malengakeku anajopalya litaji la womi ambalu Chapanga akabhalaghalili bhala bhabhumpala.
\v 13 Ngati mundu anaalengakeka ngayipwagha, “Nengakeka na Chapanga.” Maghambu Chapanga ngacheaweza kulengakeka na mahakau, wala jombi ngacheandenga mundu jokapi.
\v 14 Nambu kila mundu alengakeka chikahi paahutakika na kukoluheka na utokulelu waki mweni ghoubhi uhakau.
\v 15 Henu utokulelu uhakau ghola anaukomiki, ubheleka mahoku, na mahoku ghala anaghakomiki, ghabheleka nyiwa.
\p 
\v 16 Bhalongu bhango, ngamwikoluheka!
\v 17 Kila nhupu jejibhohakeka jejibhi jamboni na jangakukepakewa, jihuma kunani kumahunde, jihuluka kuhuma kwa Atati, joabhombiki minang'anu, ambaju kwaki njeta kung'anambuka, wala nhwili wa kung'anambuka ng'anambuka.
\v 18 Kwa mapalu ghaki mweni akatubheliki kwa lilobhi laki la chakaka, nahuli tubya mu mbekenyu ja kutumbula pachilanda ja ihumbi yaki.
\s1 Kujowana na kutenda
\p 
\v 19 Bhalongu bhango bhapalu, mkombukaje lijambu lenu! Kila mundu akubha na chipyaghu cha kujowana, nambu ngaikubha na chipyaghu cha kupwagha wala kuyoma.
\v 20 Kwa ndandi inyela yaka mundu ngacheitenda ghala ghaaghapala Chapanga.
\v 21 Henu mughaleka mahakau ghinu ghokapi na mahoku ambaghu ghapetalili kubha ghamaheli, mlibhekaje pahi jaka Chapanga na kulijopalela lilobhi lela lelipandakiki mumitima jinu, ambalu liweza kunkengalela mwehapa mabhene.
\p 
\v 22 Ngamwalikolowa mabhete kwa kulijowanela pena lilobhi laki, nambu mlihengaje kwa itendu.
\v 23 Kwa ndandi mundu jokapi joajowanela Lilobhi laka Chapanga, nambu ngacheatenda kwa itendu, jonihoju nde ngati mundu joalingalila sula jaki mu chioo.
\v 24 Maghambu alilingalila, anajomwili abhoka na chikahi chechechi ajewa ntundu moabhelile.
\v 25 Nambu mundu joakamulakila Shelia jejikamilike, jela jejileta lujeku, najombi ajendalyaye kuhenga bhenibhela panga na kujewa cheajowini, nambu alitenda, mundu jonihoju anapengalikaje mu kila chindu cheahenga.
\p 
\v 26 Ngati mundu ahambukila kubha anjojabhe Chapanga, nambu ngacheaweza kulujemalela lulimi lwaki, kunjojabhe kwaki Chapanga kwaka mundu hoyu nde pawaka, na alikolowa mwene.
\v 27 Kujojabhe kokubhi kunyahi, na kwangakubha na mahoku, kokujetakalewa palongi jaka Chapanga Atati witu, nde kongone: Kubhajangatila bhabhahweliwi na bhabheleka bhabhu na bhabhahweliwi na bhalomi mu ulali wabhu, na kulilenda na ndema panga kutenda mahoku.
\c 2
\s1 Upendeleu
\p 
\v 1 Balongu bhango, ngati munhobhale Bambo witu Yesu Kristo, Bambo wa ulumbalilu, ngamwapendale bhandu.
\v 2 Tupwagha ngati anahikiki mundu mu nyumba hinu ya kuhimanganila akabya aweti pete ya zahabu na ingobhu inyahi, kabheti kujingila mundu kahochu joabhi na ingobhu yeihakatwike,
\v 3 ngati anamumpekeha utopalela jola joaweti ingobhu inyahi na kumpwaghila: “Tama pambane pandu panyahi,” nambu kahochu jola mumpwaghi: “Wehapa ujema pala,” au “Tama pambane paluhombi, pambipi na magholu ghangu,”
\v 4 bho, ghonihoghu le nga upendeleu pachilanda jino? Bho, kutemula kwinu hoku ngachekubhokana na maholalelu ghinu mahakau?
\p 
\v 5 Bhalongu bhango bhapalu, njowanyaje! Bho, Chapanga ngacheakahawili bhahochu bha ndema ghoni bhakubhaje bhana hindu yamaheli ya uhobhalelu na bhapwelelu bha ukolongwa ghoakabhalaghile bhala bhabhumpala?
\v 6 Nambu mwehapa mubhahekatela utopelu akakahochu! Bho, bhana hindu yamaheli ngachebhumbonela mwehapa na kunhutana mbaka palongi ja pachengo?
\v 7 Bho, nga bhombi le bhabhalitondola lihina lela lelibhi linyahi laka Kristo lempekiwi mwehapa?
\p 
\v 8 Ngati anamtii Shelia yela ya Ukolongwa ngati moilembakiki mu Malembu Mahuhu, “Umpala njaku ngati moulipalila wamwene,” anankubha muhenga wichu namaa.
\v 9 Nambu anamubhapendale bhandu, mtenda mahoku, na Shelia juntemula kubha mwehapa mbi na mahoku.
\v 10 Kwa ndandi mundu joakamula Shelia jokapi, nambu anahekiti Shelia jimu pela, mundu jonihoju akubha na lihoku la kuheketa Shelia jokapi.
\v 11 Kwa ndandi jombi joakapwaghiki: “Ngawitenda ugone,” bhelabhela akapwaghiki, “Ngawikoma.” Henu anangati ngacheutenda ugone, nambu ukomiki, wehapa uhekiti Shelia.
\v 12 Henu, mpwaghaje na kuhenga ngati bhandu bhabhitemulikaje na Shelia jejileta kulijeka.
\v 13 Maghambu Chapanga ngaikubhi na chiha panaantemula mundu jwangakubha na chiha. Nambu chiha chijiweza utemulo.
\s1 Uhobhalelu na matendu
\p 
\v 14 Bhalongu bhangu, bho kubhi na nyonjeka bholi mundu kupwagha abhi na uhobhalelu nambu ngacheabhi na matendu? Bho, uhobhalelu ngati ghonihoghu uweza kunkengalela?
\v 15 Tupwagha umbona njaku, nkambaku au mbomba ngacheabhi na ingobhu wala chilebhi,
\v 16 bho, anaibhajangatya chindu bholi kubhapwaghila bhanihabha: “Njendaje kwa lukwale mkanyatukya moto na kutupila,” panga kubhapekeha ghaghapalika kwa matamu ghabhu?
\v 17 Bhelabhela, uhobhalelu kanjika jaki pangakubha na matendu, upotile.
\p 
\v 18 Nambu mundu aweza kupwagha: “Wehapa ubhi na uhobhalelu, nepani mi na matendu. Nangihaje uhobhalelu waku panga na matendu, na nepani ananukulangihaji uhobhalelu wangu kwa indela ja matendu ghangu.”
\v 19 Bho, wehapa uhobhalela kubha kubhi na Chapanga jumu pela? Ena! Nambu hata majobhi ghahobhalela leniheli, na kubhaghaja kwa choghoi.
\v 20 Ung'ang'a wenga! Bho, upala kumanya kubha uhobhalelu panga matendu upotile?
\v 21 Bho, Ibulahimu hokolu witu akahengiki bhole nahuli kujetakalewa palongi jaka Chapanga? Kwa matendu ghaki, chikahi paakambohiki mwana waki Isaka kubha nyambiku panani ya chihanja.
\v 22 Ubhona kubha uhobhalelu waki ukatendiki lihengu papamu na matendu ghaki, na kubha uhobhalelu waki ghola ukapitalili kwa indela ja matendu ghaki.
\v 23 Henu ghakapitalili Malembu ghaghapwagha: “Ibulahimu akunhobhali Chapanga, na kwa uhobhalelu waki akajetakaliwi palongi jaka Chapanga kubha mundu wambone.” Bhela Ibulahimu akalowakiki nkochi waka Chapanga.
\v 24 Mlola kubha mundu ajetakalewa palongi jaka Chapanga kwa matendu ghaki, na nga kwa uhobhalelu kanjika jaki.
\p 
\v 25 Bhelabhela, hata Lahabu nkemi jola, bho, ngacheakabhalangiki kubha ajetakaliwi palongi jaka Chapanga kwa matendu, chikahi paakabhajopali bhalalukila bha mambu bhala, na kubhajangatila kubhapiha kunja kwa indela najenge?
\p 
\v 26 Henu, ngati bhela hyegha panga roho jipotile, bhelabhela uhobhalelu panga matendu upotile.
\c 3
\s1 Lulimi
\p 
\v 1 Bhalongu bhango, bhamaheli bhinu ngamwikubha bhabhola. Ngati mommanyila, tepani tabhabhola anatutemuliwa nakanopi kupeta bhangi.
\v 2 Ndandi tabhokapi tulikobhandola mu mambu ghamaheli. Nambu ngati mundu ngacheahokeha mu kulongela kwaki, henu jonihoju nde mkamilifo, na aweza kujitawala bhelebhela hyegha jaki jokapi.
\v 3 Tepani tubhawatika falasi mighoji mumilomu jabhu nahuli kututii, na kwa indela jeniheji tuweza kubhalongoha kokapi kotupala.
\v 4 Kabhete ndingalyaje sitima papamu na kubha ngolongwa namaa, na kukangakika na mpongu ukali, nambu jiweza kulonguheka na mshikanu uchoku namaa, jijenda kokapi kola ndongoha wa sitima koapala.
\v 5 Bhelabhela lulimi, papamu nde chiungu kichoku cha hyegha, chililumbalila mambu makolongwa namaa. Ndingalyaje imuli ya moto moiweze kuyonanga chitengu chikolongwa.
\v 6 Bhelabhela lulimi nde ngati moto. Utwelili mahakau ghamaheli, lubhi na mbekenyu jaki mu hyegha hitu na kujaghanila uhakau mkati jitu tabhete. Uyonanga matamu ghitu ghokapi kwa moto ghouhuma ku Jehanamu.
\v 7 Mundu aweza kudima hinyama, na aweziki kudima ihumbi yokapi, hinyama ya muchitengu, ijuni, hinyama yeikwabha, na ihumbi ya mubahali, nayombi ijomwi kudimakika na bhandu.
\v 8 Nambu njeta mundu joaweziki kuludima lulimi. Lulimi nde chindu chihakau, ngachelutawaliwa, na lutweli chikau chechikoma.
\v 9 Kwa lulimi tepani tunchengu Chapanga Atati witu. Kwa lulimi lololu twapekeha bhandu masolu, bhandu ambabhu bhabhombakiki kwa ulenganesu waka Chapanga.
\v 10 Malobhi gha kupengalela na gha masolu ghahuma mu ndomu ghumu. Bhalongu bhango, mambu ghanihagha ngacheghapalika kugha bhenibhela.
\v 11 Bho, chemichemi jimu le jiweza kupiha machi manohu na machi gha mwinyo?
\v 12 Bhalongu bhango, bho, nkongu wa mtini le uweza kupambika zeituni, au nkongu wa mzabibu kupambika ngoju? Bhelabhela chemichemi ngachejiweza kupiha machi gha mwinyu na machi manohu.
\s1 Mbulau yeihuma kunani kumahunde
\p 
\v 13 Bho, nde nane joabhi na mbulau na malangu pachilanda jinu? Henu, alangihaje lijambu heli kwa lujendu lwaki lunyahi na kwa matendu ghaki ghambone ghaghatendakeka kwa kuliheleha na kwa mbulau.
\v 14 Nambu anamitima jinu jitweli wihu, kuhakalanila na kubaguana, bhela ngamwalilumbalila, wala ngamwipwagha upuhi panani ja chakaka.
\v 15 Mbulau ja ntundu ghonihoghu ngachejihuma kunani kumahunde, nambu nde ja kindema, nga jaka Roho Mhuhu nambu ja kishetani.
\v 16 Maghambu pokapi papabhi na wihu na milomu, panihapa nde papabhi na mbalaghana, na kila ntundu wa uhakau.
\v 17 Nambu mbulau jejihuma kunani kumahunde kutumbula nde jinyahi, kabhete jipala lukwali, ja upole, jibhi tayali kujowanela malobhi gha bhandu bhangi, jitweli chiha na matendu ghambone, jangakumpendale mundu, kabhete ngachejibhi na undumila kubhele.
\v 18 Mambu ghaghunyambiha Chapanga ghapandakika mu lukwali na bhandu bhala bhabhatenda lukwali.
\c 4
\s1 Ukochi na ndema
\p 
\v 1 Bho, kukomana ngondu kuhuma kwako, na milomu jejibhi pachilanda jinu jihuma kwako? Bho, ngachejihuma, mu matokulelu ghinu mahakau ghaghaleta ngondu mu ihungu hinu?
\v 2 Mtokulela namaa kupata hindu, wala ngachemuipata, mkoma na kubhona wihu, nambu ngamuwezi kuipata yela yemuipala, bhela mtenda kulochana na kukomana. Wala ngachempata yela yemuipala maghambu ngachemundobha Chapanga.
\v 3 Kabhete pamlobha ngachemuipata maghambu ndobha kwa maholalelu mahakau; mlobha nahuli muitumila hindu heyi kwa matokulelu ghinu.
\v 4 Mwenga bhagone! Bho, ngachemmanyi kubha nkochi na ndema nde kubha adui waka Chapanga? Henu kila joakubha nkochi wa ndema alitenda kubha adui waka Chapanga.
\v 5 Bho, muholale kubha Malembu Mahuhu ghapwagha waka paghakapwaghiki: “Roho hoju ambaju Chapanga ambekiki mkati jitu abhi na wihu nakanopi?”
\v 6 Nambu chihomu chetupekewa na Chapanga chibhi na makili nakanopi, ngati moghapwaghi Malembu Mahuhu: “Chapanga abhapenga bhabhalibhona, nambu abhapekeha chihomu bhabhaliheleha.”
\p 
\v 7 Bhela mulihelia pahi jaka Chapanga. Mumpengaje Shetani, najombi anaantilaje.
\v 8 Munheghalya Chapanga, najombi anahika pambipi na mwenga. Ngolulaje mabhoku ghinu, mwenga mwembi na mahoku! Ngolulaje mitima jinu, mwenga mwembi akandumila kubhele!
\v 9 Mbonaje huzuni, mulelaje na kuombuleza. Chiheku chinu na chibya chilelu, na chiheku chinu chibya huzuni ngolongwa!
\v 10 Muliheliyaje palongi jaka Bambo, najombi anaankwehaje.
\s1 Lilakalilu kubhokana na kubhatemu bhange
\p 
\v 11 Bhalongo ngamwipwaghanila mahakau mabhete kwa mabhete. Mundu jokapi joampwagha mahakau njaki au kuntemula, mundu hoju ajikopungane Shelia na kujitemula. Nambu paujitemu Shelia, bhela ngachewitii Shelia, nambu ujitemu Shelia.
\v 12 Chapanga kanjika jaki nde joabhekiki Shelia na kujitemula. Nde jombi kanjika jaki pela joaweza kukengalela na kuyonanga. Henu bho, wehapa nde wa nani mbaka untemu mundu jonge?
\s1 Lilakalilu kubhokana na kulibhona
\p 
\v 13 Henu njowanyaje mwenga mwempwagha: “Lalenu au chilabhu anatujendaje ku muchi agho au ghola tukatamaje monihomu chaka chimu, tuhemalaje na kulombesa na kupata nyonjeka.”
\v 14 Nambu ngachemmanyi hata matamu ghinu kwa chilabhu anaghabya bhole! Bho, womi winu nde kiki? Mwehapa nde ngati likongobha lelipitalila kwa chikahi chijipi pena na kuhobha kabhete.
\v 15 Nambu impalika kupwagha: “Ngati Bambo anapaliki, anatutamaje na kuhenga chenjenu au chela.”
\v 16 Nambu sajenu mulibhona na kulilumbalila. Kulibhona kwa ntundu ghonihoghu nde uhakau.
\p 
\v 17 Bhela, mundu jokapi joamanyi lijambu lamboni lelumpalika kulihenga, nambu ngachealihenga, mundu jonihoju atenda mahoku.
\c 5
\s1 Lilakalilu kwa bhana hindu yamaheli
\p 
\v 1 Henu njowanyaje, mwenga mwembi na hindu yamaheli! Mlelaje na kuombuleza kwa ndandi ja mang'ahiku ghinu ghaghunhikilaje!
\v 2 Umaheli wa hindu hinu ubholiki, na ingobhu hinu imemaniki na mangeki.
\v 3 Zahabu hinu na madini ghinu gha feza ijingi kutu, na kutu jaki anajundandilaje, na yeniheyi anaikula hyegha hinu ngati moto. Mwehapa mulilundakili chikoku cha hindu yamaheli mu machobha ghani gha kujomukela.
\v 4 Ndingalyaje! Ngachemwakalepiki malepu bhatumika bhabhakahengiki lihengu mu mighonda jinu. Njowanyaje mang'ong'uteku ghabhu! Na Bambo wa Manjolinjoli ajowini chilelu cha bhatumika bhabhakahengiki lihengu mu mighonda jinu.
\v 5 Mtemi pundema matamu gha kulihekeha na gha kulinyambiha. Mulinenapishi tayali mu lichobha la kuchinjakika.
\v 6 Mubhatemwili na kubhakoma bhandu bhanga na mahoku, na bhombi ngachebhakumpengiki mwenga.
\s1 Uhinakilu na malobhu
\p 
\v 7 Henu, bhalongu bhango, muhinakayaje mbaka kuhika kwaka Bambo. Ndingalyaje ntundu ndemi moalendalela imbeju ipihaje mahunu ghaaghapala nakanopi. Jombi alendalela kwa uhinakilu kwa ndandi ja kupata iyula ja kutumbula na ja kujomukela.
\v 8 Mwehapa nanamu muhinakalyaje, na kabhete njemaje kwa ukangamalu mu uhobhalelu, maghambu kuhika kwaka Bambo kuheghalile.
\p 
\v 9 Bhalongu bhango, ngamwing'ong'utekilana mabhete kwa mabhete ngamwihika kutemuliwa na Chapanga. Ndingalyaje mtemula ajemi pandyango!
\v 10 Bhalongu bhango, mkombukaye bhalota bhabhapwaghika kwa lihina laka Bambo, mlengana nabhu ngati mobhakahinakile mu mang'ahiku.
\v 11 Tubhaloha bhanihabha bhabhabhi na mbanga kwa ndandi bhakahinakili. Njowini malobhi gha uhinakilu waka Ayubu, na mmanyi ntundu Bambo moakantendile pakujomukela. Maghambu Bambo atwelili chiha na mpole.
\p 
\v 12 Nakanopi ja ghokapi, bhalongu bhango, ngamwilapa, kwa kunani kumahunde, wala kwa pundema, wala kwa chindu chengi chokapi. “Ena” yinu na ibya ena, na “Ngabhela” yinu ibya “Ngabhela” nanga bhela anamtemuliwaje na Chapanga.
\p 
\v 13 Bho, kubhi na mundu jokapi pachilanda jinu apatiki mang'ahiku? Henu impalika kulobha. Bho, kubhi na jokapi joabhi na chiheku? Henu ajembaje nyembu ya kulumbalila.
\v 14 Bho, abhi mtamwa pachilanda jinu? Impalika kubhaloha bhazee bha likanisa, nabhombi anabhundobhilaje na kumpaka mahuta kwa lihina laka Bambo.
\v 15 Anabhalobhiki kwa uhobhalelu mtamwa hoju analamaje. Bambo anampekya mbanga, na mahoku ghaatendiki anaghabhohakikaje.
\v 16 Henu, mlekakanyaje mahoku ghinu, na mlobhilanyaje, nahuli mpata kulamiswa. Malobhu ghaka mundu joajetakaliwi palongi jaka Chapanga ghabhi na makili ghamaheli, na kuhenga ghamaheli.
\v 17 Eliya akabhi mundu ngati tepani. Akalobhiki kwa ukangamalu ihula ngajitonya, najombi ngachejakatonyiki panani ja inchi kwa chikahi cha hyaka itatu na myehi sita.
\v 18 Panihapa akalobhiki kabhete, ihula jakatonyiki kuhuma kunani, na inchi jakapihiki mahunu ghaki.
\p 
\v 19 Bhalongu bhango, jumu winu anahobhiki na kuuleka uchakaka, na mundu jongi anaankelawihe,
\v 20 amanyaje kubha, mundu jola joankelawi mwana mahoku hoju kuhuma mu indela yaki ya kuhobha, anaankengalyaje mundu mwana mahoku hoju kuhuma mu nyiwa, na kutenda mahoku ghaki mundu hoju kulekakewa na Chapanga.
